data.title: The Drum - Stretford, Manchester
data.meta_description: Previously known as the Bass Drum this unusual shaped pub closed last year. McDonalds have now applied for planning permission to demolish it and build a restaurant - the council are considering their application which has received both letters of support and objections from local residents.
